#LINK UPDATED SORRY 06/21/11 Same version as on ESL

Iquitos - Aim Map - Version Contest 2011 ESL

A Counter-Strike:Source Map by Stoop23

- Game Information -
This map consists of a single bsp file. It has 20 spawn points and has a beautiful environment. This Aim map, is perfect for 2on2 or even 1on1.
This is the aim version of an existing de_blue (AngelWings multigaming) by Stoop23.
Even though there is other Aztec map, this maya map is brightness and has a new gameplay.

- Credits -
Level-Design: Stoop23.
Textures: Aztec_remake (copyright aftersource) stuff by Blade. Losttemple textures by Stard00d (With his permission). Esl Logos made by Stoop23.
Nav File: Nav file made by VALVe.
